  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0d9c\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dc3 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "University students are protesting to demand freedom for their colleagues",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A protest organized by the Inter-University Student Union was held today in front of the Colombo Fort railway station, demanding the unconditional release of all the activists imprisoned on detention orders."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [
          {
